- Update to version 2.2.4:
  * The following function is removed from the package if installed
    in Octave >= 11.1.0:
    + funm.m  (a much improved funm.m has been added to
      Octave-11.1.0)
  * Package documentation is now included in the GUI doc pane (if
    the package has been loaded).

